570
00:25:24,606 --> 00:25:30,534
♪From somewhere deep inside of me♪

571
00:25:32,531 --> 00:25:37,287
♪Her power overtakes me♪

572
00:25:37,494 --> 00:25:43,752
♪Can I keep this Midnight
