♪If I can see with the light♪

574
00:25:47,046 --> 00:25:50,095
♪I know I'll be free♪

575
00:25:50,299 --> 00:25:53,052
♪And I can start to be whole♪

576
00:25:53,218 --> 00:25:57,018
♪I can start to be me♪

577
00:25:57,222 --> 00:26:02,854
♪But instead I am
