665
00:30:10,517 --> 00:30:12,190
Applejack baru saja jatuh ke danau.

666
00:30:12,394 --> 00:30:13,270
Oh, tidak!

667
00:30:13,478 --> 00:30:15,947
Dia butuh handuk
hangat, baju kering,...

668
00:30:16,148 --> 00:30:17,741
