669
00:30:17,941 --> 00:30:19,409
Akan kuambilkan.

670
00:30:23,363 --> 00:30:24,706
Fluttershy?

671
00:30:26,617 --> 00:30:28,369
Apa yang terjadi.

672
00:30:28,577 --> 00:30:29,624
Aku tidak tahu.

673
00:30:29,828 --> 00:30:31,546
Kita sedang menghias kue.

674
00:30:31,747 --> 00:30:33,920
